>> source: https://www.biggerbolderbaking.com/homemade-extracts/
>> serves: 2 oz
>> total time: 5-6 weeks

Peel thin strips of zest from your @lemon{1}.

Place zest into your #2-fl. oz glass bottle{}.

Add @vodka{2%oz}, filling up to the neck of the bottle.

Every few days, tilt your bottle upside down to gently mix the liquid inside.

After 5-6 weeks, you have extract!
